}}\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Here's the first sample being selected, falling down into the middle panel. It's off calculating the bootstrap confidence interval. There's the interval. The target value's in the interval. In statistical language our interval has covered the true value. We'll do this a few more times. New sample, new interval. Success, we've covered the truth again. New sample, new interval, got it again.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
