}}\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
\cf3 Every time we took a sample, our interval contained the true value, but it doesn't always happen. We'll start keeping a record of the intervals we've seen and what happened. We'll drop each interval after it forms into the bottom panel. We'll colour them green if they catch the true value. Here's five more. These two have both caught the truth, so they're all green.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
