\cf3 This one missed. The interval didn't include our target (the population mean) and so we've coloured it red. Here I want to draw your attention to the coverage statistics. We've covered the truth five of the six times we've tried this. That's a success rate of 83%.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl260\sa326\partightenfactor0
